Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:58.07,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}闪光的眼瞳看透黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.36,0:01:01.70,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}令人畏惧的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:14.02,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}自出生时便一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.91,0:01:19.92,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}爱即为凶器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:27.76,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}紧抠已然沾满鲜红的胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:33.29,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}将爱埋没于伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:37.96,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}由腐败中诞生的世界所拥有的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:40.66,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}是繁华的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:44.67,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}放生抑或杀生都是我们的罪业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:47.74,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}如猪狗一般发笑 流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:50.34,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}无病呻吟的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:54.36,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}还剩下什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:57.65,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}在保护与诓骗中腐坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:00.91,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}虽生却犹如行尸走肉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:04.32,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}耀眼的心灵出现裂痕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:07.62,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}轻轻扣上心灵的扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:10.82,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}在保护与诓骗中毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:14.22,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}装作一切都了然于心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:17.47,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}追逐的却尽是缥缈的梦幻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:55.62,ED_jap4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}我们是没有容身之处的亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:21:59.06,ED_jap4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}凭空于世的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:05.89,ED_jap2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}心失くしたわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:17.50,ED_jap2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}ただ想い出すのが怖いような気になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:25.03,ED_jap3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}忘れかけてた温もりは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.93,0:22:35.71,ED_jap3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}掴もうとした手をすり抜けた幻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:43.22,ED_jap1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}押し潰されそうになりながらも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:53.06,ED_jap1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}もう一度新しい明日を見たいと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:59.68,ED_jap4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\blur1.5}Transparent {\fnsimhei\fs20}…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:02.18,ED_jap1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}Transparent {\fnsimhei\fs20}…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:08.90,ED_jap2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}Transparent {\fnsimhei\fs20}…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:12.02,ED_jap1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)\blur1.5}Transparent {\fnsimhei\fs20}…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.63,0:23:18.39,ED_jap4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}透明になってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:05.89,ED_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}并非丢失了心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:17.50,ED_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}只是对过去的记忆心存恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:25.03,ED_cht3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}游走在忘却边缘的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.93,0:22:35.71,ED_cht3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}那是渴望拥有却无法握紧的幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:43.22,ED_cht1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}即使濒临崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:53.06,ED_cht1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur1.5}也想再次一睹崭新明天的风采
